What you need to know:

NPCK normally conducts potato marketing forums in producing counties where farmers and buyers engage in business-to-business (B2B) sessions.Although there are 61 registered varieties in the Potato Variety Catalogue, 2019 only about 24 are produced locally.The recently launched Warehouse Receipting System Council (WRSC) will also help in implementation of the potato regulations.To cushion farmers, there are accurate weather forecast apps, water-holding substances such as Zeba products and drought-resistant varieties such as Unica.